title: Method declarations can be formatted by listing the arguments vertically, or by a new line and +8 extra spaces

inline_content.Text: Method declarations can be formatted by listing the arguments vertically, or by a new line and +8 extra spaces

title: If a throws clause needs to be wrapped, put the line break in front of the throws clause and make sure it stands out from the argument list, either by indenting +8 relative to the function declaration, or +8 relative to the previous line.
